source: tests/metrics_regression.rs
expression: session_grouped
---
Session Metrics
Average user prompts = average user prompts per session
Avg time to first accepted change = minutes from session start to first accepted code change
Debug loop rate = debug-loop session rate
Error paste rate = mid-session error-paste rate
Session-to-commit rate = session end + 4h commit rate
No-output session rate = sessions with no accepted code changes

